thread.title: Ioan Prata

author: Ioan Prata
title: Ioan Prata
text:
Used the services of SunaRomania for a while now, pretty happy with the quality of the connection and the clarity of the voice. At the peak hours it might be lacking quality, sometimes but just put the phone down and ring again and you'll have a normal, good connection most of the time!
Pricewise it beats nearly everything on the market (is true, it depends on the destination, I don't know all their prices but for what I'm using it it is cheap!)
Would definitely keep on using and recommend it!
